# Live client financials — keep in the Dropbox finance lane, never in git
tools/populi-billing-extract/*.xlsx

# Local working archive - client financials, student data, proprietary docs. Never in git.
# Exception: Claude Workspace job specs, Context/, and Outputs/ are repo assets the
# scheduled jobs read and write (Context/ and Outputs/ files were already tracked; the
# old rules only blocked NEW files there, which stranded every scheduled run's output).
Open Items/*
!Open Items/Claude Workspace/
Open Items/Claude Workspace/*
!Open Items/Claude Workspace/SWEEP.md
!Open Items/Claude Workspace/SCHEDULES.md
!Open Items/Claude Workspace/Daily Curation.md
!Open Items/Claude Workspace/Context/
!Open Items/Claude Workspace/Outputs/
